name: Wukong
description: Wukong, inspired by the character Sun Wukong from Journey to the West, is a collection of Memecoins and NFTs deployed on the Solana blockchain,Holding NFTs can bring numerous benefits, such as receiving airdrops of Wukong tokens,Obtain one Sun Wukong picture frame with a personal signature. Wukong embodies the fusion of Web3 technology and Chinese mythology, contributing to the promotion and preservation of traditional Chinese culture.
